      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 13,
      "message": "This has to be increased. A \"error = java.net.SocketTimeoutException: Read timed out\" is thrown at Context Aggregator, because it does not receive response form NDCTXT builder in 15 seconds.  \nMy tests take less than 20 seconds.  \nTested successfully with 50 seconds (both timeouts set to 50000).",
